We lose our bearings following these Knights and ladies;
to live in this (t is) prehistoric (prehistroic) land we must shed (sehd) many habits
of thought (thoght); but after all it is not an unreal world;
a fabricated world; it still exists in us, deep sunk,
savage, primitive; m remembered.

Brother Cosroe, I find myself aggrieved,
Yet insufficient to (yto) express the same;
For it requires a great and thundering speech

It is bombast, it is pageantry (pagenatry); it is hyperbole. And yet
puissant (pusis ant), Words mount (mout); pile on top of each other (ther);
surpass common sense; clash (clah) and rebound:
